snippet.title: Starship Troopers: Terran Command - Raising Hell | Trailer video
snippet.description:
Get ready to dive into the fiery chaos of planet Gehenna. Explore the struggle on this molten hellscape, centered around Vilon Station and the Mobile Infantry's mission to protect humanity from the relentless Arachnid hordes. Take command of the Mobile Infantry and do your part!
